WEBVTT

00:00:00.056 --> 00:00:45.557
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:54.125 --> 00:00:55.208
All of this

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.541
was your scheme.

00:00:57.916 --> 00:00:58.833
Yes.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.125
Why?

00:01:00.583 --> 00:01:01.625
Why?

00:01:01.791 --> 00:01:04.791
The throne should have been mine from the start.

00:01:05.750 --> 00:01:08.625
But the late emperor took it from me.

00:01:09.208 --> 00:01:10.458
Everything I’ve done

00:01:10.625 --> 00:01:13.250
was to reclaim what was rightfully mine.

00:01:13.291 --> 00:01:15.000
So, the Liuxiang Pavilion in Luoyang

00:01:15.333 --> 00:01:17.083
and the Changan County Gambling Den

00:01:17.583 --> 00:01:18.833
you knew about them all along.

00:01:21.333 --> 00:01:23.250
Eunuch Qiu wanted to use these two places

00:01:23.416 --> 00:01:26.458
to control officials both in and out of court.

00:01:26.875 --> 00:01:28.375
How could I not know?

00:01:28.833 --> 00:01:30.125
How long have you been planning this?

00:01:31.416 --> 00:01:33.041
Sending us into the palace to steal the mirror

00:01:33.666 --> 00:01:34.916
was also part of your plan.

00:01:35.041 --> 00:01:35.958
That's right.

00:01:36.208 --> 00:01:37.166
Everything

00:01:37.333 --> 00:01:39.375
was within my calculations.

00:01:39.750 --> 00:01:41.375
Having you do these things

00:01:41.458 --> 00:01:42.875
was simply convenient

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.291
for me to monitor your every move.

00:01:45.583 --> 00:01:47.416
So that Qiu De would trust

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:48.958
the matter of the Xuanyuan Mirror.

00:01:50.833 --> 00:01:52.000
All along,

00:01:52.041 --> 00:01:53.416
he was just one step away from usurping the throne.

00:01:53.500 --> 00:01:55.541
He only needed a final spark.

00:01:55.666 --> 00:01:56.958
And this mirror

00:01:57.625 --> 00:02:00.291
was the fuse I prepared for him.

00:02:03.041 --> 00:02:04.166
What a pity.

00:02:04.291 --> 00:02:06.958
Eunuch Qiu never imagined

00:02:07.375 --> 00:02:09.916
the palace banquet coup he plotted

00:02:10.958 --> 00:02:13.000
would end up benefiting me.

00:02:13.125 --> 00:02:14.125
Foster father,

00:02:15.166 --> 00:02:16.625
you truly are mad.

00:02:16.708 --> 00:02:18.083
This is treason.

00:02:18.291 --> 00:02:19.958
This is following the will of heaven.

00:02:21.208 --> 00:02:23.541
The Tang Dynasty is on the brink of collapse.

00:02:23.916 --> 00:02:25.625
The people need a savior.

00:02:25.666 --> 00:02:27.291
to restore the Tang Dynasty.

00:02:27.666 --> 00:02:28.791
And I

00:02:29.375 --> 00:02:31.375
am the most suitable person for that.

00:02:31.458 --> 00:02:32.708
You don’t have to sit on the throne

00:02:32.750 --> 00:02:34.250
to serve the country and its people.

00:02:37.250 --> 00:02:38.583
All these years,

00:02:38.791 --> 00:02:40.958
I kept telling myself

00:02:41.416 --> 00:02:43.416
to be a good subject,

00:02:43.541 --> 00:02:45.291
to fulfill my duty,

00:02:45.416 --> 00:02:46.500
to serve the nation and the people,

00:02:46.583 --> 00:02:47.875
and not to fight for anything.

00:02:49.375 --> 00:02:50.750
But in the end,

00:02:50.916 --> 00:02:53.416
the court declined and eunuchs took power.

00:02:53.916 --> 00:02:54.916
Jingnian,

00:02:55.125 --> 00:02:56.541
you must believe me.

00:02:56.833 --> 00:02:58.083
Only I

00:02:58.250 --> 00:03:00.500
am worthy of the throne.

00:03:03.666 --> 00:03:05.583
When I ascend the throne,

00:03:06.041 --> 00:03:08.708
the scholars of Guming Villa

00:03:09.125 --> 00:03:13.000
will praise my virtue and legitimacy to the world.

00:03:13.208 --> 00:03:15.833
The Xuanyuan Mirror, in accordance with heaven,

00:03:16.291 --> 00:03:18.333
will grant me imperial authority.

00:03:18.541 --> 00:03:20.000
The hearts of all under heaven

00:03:20.166 --> 00:03:21.666
will submit to me.

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:22.625
So,

00:03:23.458 --> 00:03:25.916
this was your true purpose in taking over Guming Villa.

00:03:27.208 --> 00:03:28.500
You had planned it all along

00:03:29.291 --> 00:03:31.416
to have those scholars serve your grand plan.

00:03:32.208 --> 00:03:34.125
To spread word of your ambitions.

00:03:34.541 --> 00:03:35.708
If I’m not mistaken,

00:03:36.125 --> 00:03:38.666
the book "Treatise on Governing the State" held by Magistrate Sun of Fuping County

00:03:39.458 --> 00:03:40.833
was also given to you, wasn’t it?

00:03:40.958 --> 00:03:41.583
Yes.

00:03:41.666 --> 00:03:42.500
That's right.

00:03:42.750 --> 00:03:43.958
Use people as tools,

00:03:44.125 --> 00:03:45.750
and one can attain the way of immortals.

00:03:45.958 --> 00:03:47.500
But use the state as a tool,

00:03:47.791 --> 00:03:50.250
and one can rule all under heaven.

00:03:57.458 --> 00:03:59.041
General, please step aside.

00:04:07.500 --> 00:04:08.458
Young hero Lin,

00:04:09.208 --> 00:04:11.083
I advise you to stay here quietly.

00:04:11.916 --> 00:04:13.458
At least you’ll have a chance to live.

00:04:17.166 --> 00:04:18.083
Fine.

00:04:18.750 --> 00:04:19.541
I

00:04:20.041 --> 00:04:21.291
will stay here.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.250
But what about Li Jingnian?

00:04:31.333 --> 00:04:32.791
He’s almost finished, isn’t he?

00:04:44.750 --> 00:04:45.708
Take him down.

00:05:54.708 --> 00:05:55.916
Lin Xiaoran

00:06:18.250 --> 00:06:19.375
So

00:06:20.500 --> 00:06:22.000
That Xuanyuan Mirror

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:25.250
will reveal the true dragon’s visage no matter who looks into it.

00:06:26.250 --> 00:06:27.541
You just need to

00:06:27.583 --> 00:06:30.125
show your dragon’s visage to all the officials at the palace banquet.

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:32.541
Then your plan will succeed, right?

00:06:34.250 --> 00:06:35.083
Yes.

00:06:35.250 --> 00:06:36.625
You’re absolutely right.

00:06:36.833 --> 00:06:37.208
Foster father

00:06:37.250 --> 00:06:38.083
Enough.

00:06:46.791 --> 00:06:47.708
Qiuwan

00:06:50.125 --> 00:06:51.041
Where is Lin Xiaoran?

00:06:51.458 --> 00:06:52.250
What have you done to him?

00:06:52.291 --> 00:06:54.541
I know you can’t accept all this.

00:06:55.208 --> 00:06:57.333
But my patience is limited.

00:06:57.791 --> 00:06:59.458
If you don’t help me,

00:07:00.333 --> 00:07:01.875
I’ll kill her.

00:07:07.416 --> 00:07:08.875
I’m giving you

00:07:09.083 --> 00:07:10.750
only one chance.

00:07:18.333 --> 00:07:19.500
Lin Xiaoran

00:07:19.708 --> 00:07:21.500
The righteous path you hold onto

00:07:21.708 --> 00:07:23.166
I will fulfill it for you.

00:07:44.875 --> 00:07:45.708
Qiuwan

00:07:46.041 --> 00:07:47.041
Qiuwan

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:50.625
Qiuwan

00:07:50.875 --> 00:07:51.875
Qiuwan

00:07:53.833 --> 00:07:54.833
Qiuwan

00:07:55.458 --> 00:07:56.541
Shen Qiuwan

00:07:57.041 --> 00:07:58.250
Shen Qiuwan

00:08:10.833 --> 00:08:12.666
The Tang Dynasty belongs to the people.

00:08:14.250 --> 00:08:16.166
It’s not yours.

00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:21.875
It’s the Emperor.

00:08:22.041 --> 00:08:23.250
The Emperor is here.

00:08:23.583 --> 00:08:24.666
It’s the Emperor.

00:08:24.875 --> 00:08:26.625
The Emperor has arrived.

00:08:29.208 --> 00:08:30.791
Emperor! Emperor!

00:09:12.958 --> 00:09:14.958
This is the legendary Xuanyuan Mirror.

00:09:15.666 --> 00:09:17.375
If our Emperor obtains this mirror,

00:09:17.833 --> 00:09:20.125
he is the chosen savior of Heaven.

00:09:23.833 --> 00:09:25.708
Heaven blesses the Tang Dynasty.

00:09:25.791 --> 00:09:30.166
Long live the Emperor!

00:10:11.625 --> 00:10:12.541
Lord Li

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:15.041
I'm investigating supernatural cases among the common folk.

00:10:15.375 --> 00:10:17.166
Wherever evil spirits arise,

00:10:17.291 --> 00:10:18.791
you'll find me, Lin Xiaoran.

00:10:19.458 --> 00:10:20.375
Lin Xiaoran.

00:10:20.791 --> 00:10:22.458
I’m giving you two choices now.

00:10:22.583 --> 00:10:23.125
First,

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:24.250
stay and help me with the investigation.

00:10:24.291 --> 00:10:25.166
I choose the second.

00:10:25.375 --> 00:10:26.375
Be generous, be generous, be generous.

00:10:26.416 --> 00:10:27.458
Don’t push it.

00:10:27.541 --> 00:10:28.750
Lin Xiaoran and I

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.166
have been orphans since childhood.

00:10:30.250 --> 00:10:31.375
We’ve endured endless humiliation.

00:10:31.666 --> 00:10:32.791
Wandering the world with a sword

00:10:32.958 --> 00:10:34.416
is my choice.

00:10:35.041 --> 00:10:36.166
Everyone

00:10:36.333 --> 00:10:38.000
has their own mission.

00:10:39.875 --> 00:10:41.541
Take my boss and leave first.

00:10:41.708 --> 00:10:43.000
Luo Han.

00:10:47.541 --> 00:10:48.583
Li Jingnian.

00:10:49.291 --> 00:10:50.708
Once this is over,

00:10:51.041 --> 00:10:52.416
come join me for an adventure in the martial world.

00:11:04.041 --> 00:11:04.916
Hey.

00:11:10.166 --> 00:11:11.916
Now that the world is at peace,

00:11:12.083 --> 00:11:14.125
do you want to join me for some fun in the martial world?

00:11:20.083 --> 00:11:21.125
Sure.